    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/ac2a885f4376983c46f1fe0a35aed7d2.avif?t=1762802535\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras_big/ac2a885f4376983c46f1fe0a35aed7d2.avif?t=1762802535 width=800 height=224 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Follow us on X and go to our website to subscribe to get listed for Alpha Playtest and get a free permanent pet!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Aetherian Chronicles is a 3D Casual SideScroller MMORPG focused on interaction with AI controlled players. Explore, train, party up, make friends and trade with real people or AI controlled players! After a hard day of grinding monsters or hunting bosses, wind down by chatting other AI or real players, or dance! It's your adventure, do whatever you feel like it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/2fb784fc45758bb44d4c0edf480f9f01.poster.avif?t=1762802535\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/2fb784fc45758bb44d4c0edf480f9f01.webm?t=1762802535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/2fb784fc45758bb44d4c0edf480f9f01.mp4?t=1762802535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight Gigantic bosses and monsters</strong>: Participate in boss runs or kill legendary monsters for your quests! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/cb518587c25d915b44a8296c6aea6310.poster.avif?t=1762802535\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/cb518587c25d915b44a8296c6aea6310.webm?t=1762802535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/cb518587c25d915b44a8296c6aea6310.mp4?t=1762802535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Work with AI or Real Players</strong>: Chat, party up and make friends! Everything is easier when you work as a team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/f9f9a9b132874d2f7ad5eb5eb0eb68c9.poster.avif?t=1762802535\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/f9f9a9b132874d2f7ad5eb5eb0eb68c9.webm?t=1762802535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/f9f9a9b132874d2f7ad5eb5eb0eb68c9.mp4?t=1762802535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the Serene World of Aetherian Haven</strong>: Indulge yourself in the lore and quests from NPCs with a spicy personality!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/71fff4807348e6290b4311b84a8b43b8.poster.avif?t=1762802535\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/71fff4807348e6290b4311b84a8b43b8.webm?t=1762802535\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3060390/extras/71fff4807348e6290b4311b84a8b43b8.mp4?t=1762802535\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grind your way through the monster galore</strong>: Mechnical monkeys, blue kittens or pink sponges, level up and discover the many monsters that call Aetherian Haven home!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the world of Aetherian Chronicles. Enjoy diverse environments as you navigate through Castle Keep, Joyful Grasslands, Green Thickets, Barren Chasms and a dark and swampy cave hosting the dangerous Worm Boss! Aetherian Chronicles offer you a wealth of gameplay, whatever your style!</p>",
